title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Recently elected to non-resident membership in the Overseas Press Club of America was an editor of a Chinese medical journal who rejoices in the name of Young Sick Kim! [K.S. Giniger, New York]
